缓存管理</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/</link><description>Recent content in 缓存管理 on Cloudpods</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Dec 2021 10:38:08 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs: 查看缓存</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/list/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Dec 2021 19:35:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/list/</guid><description>
&lt;p>查看自动快照策略缓存到的平台等信息&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>在自动快照策略页面，单击自动快照策略名称项，进入自动快照策略详情页面。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>单击“缓存列表”页签，进入缓存页面。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>查看自动快照策略的缓存列表信息，包括策略名称、状态、创建时间、更新时间、平台、区域、云账号等。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Docs: 删除缓存</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/delete/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Dec 2021 10:39:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/compute/snapshot/tutorial/snapshotpolicy/cache/delete/</guid><description>
&lt;p>删除缓存即删除对应公有云平台上的自动快照策略。仅未关联硬盘的缓存支持删除。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>在自动快照策略页面，单击自动快照策略名称项，进入自动快照策略详情页面。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>单击“缓存列表”页签，进入缓存页面。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>单击缓存右侧操作列 &lt;strong>&lt;em>&amp;ldquo;删除&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em>&lt;/strong> 按钮，弹出操作确认对话框。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>单击 &lt;strong>&lt;em>&amp;ldquo;确定&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em>&lt;/strong> 按钮，完成操作。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item></channel></rss>